      • Book

        public Book(java.lang.String title,
            java.lang.String author,
            boolean canBeBorrowedByAnyone,
            long id,
            boolean availableForBorrow)
        Constructs a Book with the specified title, author and type. Forces the ID to be at least the specified one. Should never be called to create a new book.
        Parameters:
        title - the title of the book to be created
        author - the author of the book to be created
        canBeBorrowedByAnyone - the type of the book (true for General type and false for Text type)
        id - the id to be forced upon the book
